  <title>Tagging Tasks</title>

  <p>A tag is a simple word that begins with the <em style="strong">@</em> sign.</p>

  <p>When you type a word beginning with <em style="strong">@</em>, it is displayed with yellow highlighting, which is the indicator that <app>GTG</app> considers the word to be a tag. You have the option to associate tags with custom colors. Tags are displayed with any associated custom color in the <gui>Task Editor</gui>. See <link xref="gtg-tag-color">Editing Tag Properties</link> for more information. You can select a tag while working in the <gui>Task Editor</gui> to view all other associated tasks in the <gui>Task Browser</gui>.</p>

