  <p>You can use tags to sort your tasks. Tags are viewable in the <gui>Sidebar</gui>. You can enable the <gui>Sidebar</gui> from the <gui>Main Menu</gui> on the <gui>Headerbar</gui>. This displays all of the tags that you have created. When a tag is selected, all tasks that are associated with that tag are displayed. A task can have an unlimited number of tags.</p>

<p>See the following sections for information on how to create and personalize tags.</p>

